User icon: kirby_obrien
Kirby O&#39;Brien
HI Hugh, Great job! I&#39;m a good guinea pig because I had not seen this. It took me a while to analyze the poster to understand what it was about and how it was organized. My one thought is could you provide examples of an&#34;abstract character&#34; of a &#34;glyph&#34; or maybe just a small portion of a unicode chart. You have good information to people who might already know what the words mean but if your audience is for new or untrained people they may not know the tech talk. Just a few thoughts take or leave them they were free!!

